---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Join the Club">
  
  <div class="relative bg-gray-900 text-white py-20 px-4 rounded-b-3xl md:rounded-2xl mb-12 shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img 
        src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/images/hero2.jpg`} 
        alt="Club Field" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40" 
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-900 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">Become a Member</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto drop-shadow-md">
        From first flight to aerobatic master. Join Macon County's premier aviation community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-full shadow-sm text-4xl">üõ©Ô∏è</div>
      <div class="flex-grow text-center md:text-left">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">Never flown before?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Don't buy a plane yet!</strong> We offer free introductory flights using our club trainer planes. 
          We use a "Buddy Box" system that links two controllers, so an instructor can take over instantly if you get in trouble. 
          It's 100% safe and free.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">
        Schedule a Demo
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">Ready to Join? (3 Simple Steps)</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md border-l-8 border-primary">
          <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-primary text-white font-bold text-xl rounded-full">1</div>
          <div class="grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Join the AMA</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              All members must hold a current membership with the Academy of Model Aeronautics (AMA) for insurance purposes.
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.modelaircraft.org/join" target="_blank" class="inline-block text-sm font-bold text-primary hover:text-primary-hover underline">
              Sign up at ModelAircraft.org &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md border-l-8 border-blue-500">
          <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-xl rounded-full">2</div>
          <div class="grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Complete FAA TRUST Test</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Required by the FAA for all recreational RC pilots. It takes about 15 minutes, is free, and impossible to fail.
            </p>
            <a href="https://trust.modelaircraft.org/" target="_blank" class="inline-block text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">
              Take the Free Test Here &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md border-l-8 border-green-500">
          <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-green-500 text-white font-bold text-xl rounded-full">3</div>
          <div class="grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Submit Application</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              We offer two ways to join. The <strong>Online Form</strong> is preferred for faster processing.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-4">
              <a 
                href="https://forms.gle/D1zHh1EAFRBTMMy39" 
                target="_blank"
                class="inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-2 bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors shadow-sm"
              >
                Apply Online Now &rarr;
              </a>

              <a 
                href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}assets/documents/application.pdf`} 
                download="MaconAeroModelers_Application.pdf"
                class="inline-flex justify-center items-center gap-2 bg-white text-gray-700 border border-gray-300 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
                </svg>
                Download PDF
              </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm text-gray-600 border border-gray-200">
              <p class="font-bold mb-1">Mailing a check?</p>
              <p>Macon Aero Modelers<br>c/o Jim Dowdle (Treasurer)<br>359 Fulcher Vista Drive<br>Franklin, NC 28734</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">What Happens Next?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center">
            
            <div class="relative p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-2">üìù</div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">1. Apply</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Submit form & pay dues</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300">‚ûú</div>

            <div class="relative p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-2">üîç</div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">2. Review</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Treasurer verifies AMA & Payment</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300">‚ûú</div>

            <div class="relative p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-2">‚öñÔ∏è</div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">3. Vote</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Board reviews application (48 hrs)</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300">‚ûú</div>

            <div class="relative p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-green-100 bg-green-50">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-2">‚úÖ</div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-green-800">4. Welcome</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-green-700 mt-1">Receive email & start flying!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4 italic">
            * You are officially a member upon receipt of your Welcome Package email.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span>ü§ù</span> Member Commitments
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 text-sm">
                Membership in Macon Aero Modelers is more than just access to a runway. Our dues cover operating costs, but our community runs on participation.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-primary mt-1">‚óè</span>
                    <span><strong>Participation:</strong> Members are expected to help with field maintenance, work days, fundraising, and meetings when possible.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-primary mt-1">‚óè</span>
                    <span><strong>Probation:</strong> All new members are subject to a 30-day probationary period.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-primary mt-1">‚óè</span>
                    <span><strong>Refunds:</strong> If an application is denied by the Board, dues will be fully refunded.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span>üíµ</span> Annual Dues
            </h3>
            <table class="min-w-full">
                <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
                    <tr>
                        <td class="py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Open Membership</td>
                        <td class="py-3 text-right font-bold text-primary">$100.00/yr</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500" colspan="2">Standard adult membership (19+)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="py-3 font-bold text-gray-900 pt-6">Junior Membership</td>
                        <td class="py-3 text-right font-bold text-green-600 pt-6">$15.00/yr</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="py-3 text-sm text-gray-500" colspan="2">Pilots under age 19 (AMA Required)</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="mt-6 p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg text-xs text-blue-800">
                <strong>Pro-rated Dues:</strong> New members joining after July 1st pay only $50.00 for the remainder of the year.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do I need to own a plane to start?
            <span class="text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            No! We highly recommend you do NOT buy a plane until you talk to us. We have club trainer planes available for you to try.
          </p>
        </details>
        
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do you fly drones/quadcopters?
            <span class="text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Yes! We welcome fixed-wing, helicopters, and drones. We have a dedicated group of FPV pilots who fly regularly.
          </p>
        </details>

         <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Can I just show up at the field?
            <span class="text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Spectators are always welcome! However, to fly, you must be a member or a guest pilot with current AMA insurance you can fly for up to 3 days without joining the club.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>